This repository (opendia) reproduces the in-browser MCP tool surface of
agent-browser as a capability target. No source code is vendored here other
than this attribution; the locked-sha source is cloned by Everywhere's
`bench/runner/run-ab.sh` during baseline freeze (spec
`docs/specs/everywhere-replace-agent-browser.md` §5.1, Phase 0.5).

